1. Oni su *povezani* preko društvenih mreža. (They are *connected* through social media.)
2. *Povezana* je nova autoputna deonica s gradom. (The new highway section is *connected* with the city.)
3. Čovek je *povezan* s prirodom. (Man is *connected* with nature.)
4. *Povezanost* između zdravlja i ishrane je dobro poznata. (The *connection* between health and nutrition is well known.)
5. Kompanija je *povezana* s nekoliko dobavljača. (The company is *connected* with several suppliers.)
6. *Povežite* kabl s televizorom. ( *Connect* the cable to the TV.)
7. Njih dvoje su *povezani* kumstvom. (The two of them are *connected* through godparenthood.)
8. Pokušaćemo da *povežemo* različite ideje u jedan projekat. (We will try to *connect* different ideas into one project.)
9. Među ovim događajima nema *povezanosti*. (There is no *connection* among these events.)
10. Kako da *povežem* ovaj štampač sa računarom? (How can I *connect* this printer to the computer?)